@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="panel-header">
            <h2>Electricity</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
            <h3>Spot Market Analysis</h3>
            <p>
                Various key observations about the supply and demand system curves (such as sensitivity analysis).
                Supply curve generation components, marginal costs and other relevant analytics.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/EnergyMarkets/SpotCurvesAnalysis">Supply & Demand Analysis &raquo;</a>
            </p>
            <h3>Day-Ahead price forecasting</h3>
            <p>
                High accuracy day-ahead price forecasting based on a multivariate model including a wide array of
                variables(e.g. wind, gas) and market information (e.g. outages), all based on flexible parameters.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/EnergyMarkets/SpotPriceForecast">Day-Ahead Forecast &raquo;</a>
            </p>
            <h3>Forward Market Analysis</h3>
            <p>
                Modelling and simulation of all foward market (forward contracts) based on a model
                that matches information from the whole structure (e.g. options, emissions) and multiple time resolutions.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/EnergyMarkets/ForwardMarketAnalysis">Forward Analysis &raquo;</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="panel-header">
            <h2>Gas</h2>
        </div><div class="panel">
            <h3>Natural Gas Storage</h3>
            <p>
                Valuation of natural gas storage facilities under various specifications. Notable is the ability to see greeks values in
                real time, display dynamic values and so on...
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/GasMarket/StorageValuation">Storage Valuation &raquo;</a>
            </p>
            <h3>Swing Contracts</h3>
            <p>
                An advanced model providing flexibility to swing valuation, in includes a dynamic term structure, underlying
                model flexibility and a variety of nice features such as drag-and-drop interactions and a simple interface.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/GasMarkets/ForwardCurves">Swing... &raquo;</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="panel-header">
            <h2>Cross-commodities</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
            <h3>Risk Management VaR</h3>
            <p>
                A comprehensive method for calulating VaR values based on flexible distribution settings and a hybrid
                market model, providing high accuracy and extensive settings...
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/RiskManagement/PlantPortfolio">Plants VaR... &raquo;</a>
            </p>
            <h3>Virtual Power Plant</h3>
            <p>
                A simple demonstration of a virtual power plant using a multi-fuel that relies on real time data
                and highly customizable parameters.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="/RiskManagement/PlantPortfolio">VPP &raquo;</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

